  "text": "Transient trans association of allelic imprinted loci, associated with Prader-Willi syndrome and Angelman syndrome was observed in cells from normal, but not affected individuals [CITATION_1] , but the effect was later attributed to the influence of nucleolus organizer region on three-dimensional organization of the nucleus [CITATION_2] .",
